################ FORGOT-JENKINS-USERNAME-AND-PASSWORD #####################
*ssh jenkins
*cd /var/lib/jenkins
*ls
*sudo vi config.xml
*To change 10th line "<usesecurity>true</usesecurity>" to "<usesecurity>false</usesecurity>" and save
*sudo systemctl restart jenkins

*ip:8080 it open
*dashboard - manage jenkins - configure global security - security realm (none to jenkins own user database) save and apply
*dashboard - manage jenkins - manage users - delect the forgot user and creat new user

*suppose forgot only password then go ""dashboard - people - select user - cofigure - give new password - save & login""

*the changes what we do in ui jenkins it will reflect in background (vi config.xml) 
